## Description {#details}

Collection of DBG&#95;VALUEs observed when traversing a block.

Records each variable and the value the DBG&#95;VALUE refers to. Requires the machine value location dataflow algorithm to have run already, so that values can be identified.

Definition at line 1036 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/lib/codegen/livedebugvalues/instrrefbasedimpl-h">InstrRefBasedImpl.h</a>.

### Vars {#a74b0a01b154dab18a9a6b54fd737bcff}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>SmallMapVector&lt;DebugVariableID, DbgValue, 8&gt; LiveDebugValues::VLocTracker::Vars</>}>
Map <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/debugvariable">DebugVariable</a> to the latest <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/value">Value</a> it&#39;s defined to have.

Needs to be a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mapvector">MapVector</a> because we determine order-in-the-input-MIR from the order in this container. (FIXME: likely no longer true as the ordering is now provided by <a href="/docs/api/classes/livedebugvalues/debugvariablemap">DebugVariableMap</a>). We only retain the last <a href="/docs/api/classes/livedebugvalues/dbgvalue">DbgValue</a> in each block for each variable, to determine the blocks live-out variable value. The Vars container forms the transfer function for this block, as part of the dataflow analysis. The movement of values between locations inside of a block is handled at a much later stage, in the <a href="/docs/api/classes/transfertracker">TransferTracker</a> class.

Definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/lib/codegen/livedebugvalues/instrrefbasedimpl-h/#l01049">1049</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/lib/codegen/livedebugvalues/instrrefbasedimpl-h">InstrRefBasedImpl.h</a>.
</MemberDefinition>
